$$f[n]=\sum_{target\ge number[i] }f[target-number[i]]$$&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://leetcode.com/problems/count-all-valid-pickup-and-delivery-options/&#34;&gt;1359&lt;/a&gt; Count All Valid Pickup and Delivery Options&lt;/li&gt;
